Name: Out Bike the Tsunami™
About the game: Out Bike the Tsunami is an endless runner game based on true story. Bike through a platformer stage with obstacles throw at you while avoiding getting caught by the tsunami. Use ← ↑ → ↓ keys to control Ian's movement. Good luck.
